    SOURCE-LINUX: https://nodejs.org/dist/v14.17.0/node-v14.17.0-linux-x64.tar.xz
COMMANDS: tar xzf node-bin; cd node; mv lib/* /usr/local/shade/lib; mv bin/* /usr/local/shade/bin; mv include/* /usr/local/shade/include; mv share/* /usr/local/shade/share
